drivers/rtc/rtc-vr41xx.c: fix checkpatch warnings

Fixes the following warnings:
  WARNING: Use #include <linux/io.h> instead of <asm/io.h>
  WARNING: Use #include <linux/uaccess.h> instead of <asm/uaccess.h>

